The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Norman Rollins, Jr., Appellant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed. Counsel’s application to withdraw granted (see, People v Crawford, 71 AD2d 38). (Appeal from judgment of Monroe County Court, Celli, J.—assault, second degree, and unlawful imprisonment, first degree.) Present—Dillon, P. J., Callahan, Boomer, Balio and Lawton, JJ.
